<div><strong>Admission Requirements </strong></div>
<div><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br /><strong>Currently admitted to BYU-Idaho:</strong></div>
<div><strong>&nbsp;</strong><br />If you are currently admitted to BYU-Idaho, no application is necessary. Simply register for classes.</div>
<br />
<div><strong>Not currently admitted to BYU-Idaho: </strong></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<br />
<div>Important Guidelines:<br />1. You must be a high school graduate or GED recipient.</div>
<div>2. If still in high school, please see the information for <a class="intLink" href="x41337.xml">Concurrent Enrollment</a>.</div>
<div>3. All parts of the Continuing Education Application must be received two weeks prior to the first day of the semester in which you wish to enroll.</div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<br />
<div><strong>Required Application Materials:</strong></div>
<div>
<ul>
<li>Part 1 - Student Information</li>
<li>Part 2 - School Selection</li>
<li>Part 3 - Student Commitment &amp; Ecclesiastical Endorsement</li>
<li>$35 Application Fee (if applicant has never applied to Ricks or BYU-Idaho)</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>4. If you skip a semester, you must reapply.</div>
<div>5. You are not eligible for many full-time student services including housing. You are not eligible to live in approved housing and must make other arrangements. For assistance, contact the Housing Department at 208-496-9220.</div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<br />
<div><strong>You can access the application at <a href="http://www.besmart.com">www.besmart.com</a>.</strong></div>
<div></div>
<br />
<div>For admissions questions please call the <a class="intLink" href="x16732.xml" title="Admissions Office Website" target="_blank">Admissions Office</a> at 208-496-1300 or email us: <a href="mailto:admissions@byui.edu" title="Admissions Office Email">admissions@byui.edu</a>. You can even <a class="extLink" href="https://server.iad.liveperson.net/hc/1132447/?cmd=file&amp;file=visitorWantsToChat&amp;site=1132447&amp;SESSIONVAR!skill=Admissions&amp;imageUrl=https://web.byui.edu/admissions/liveperson/large&amp;referrer=http%3A//www2.byui.edu/Admissions/" title="Live Chat" target="_blank">chat with us online</a>.</div>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="List" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="Facebook;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/><!--071613 xpowercomponent_Optional to xPower--></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x25152" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"